  "body": "\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Gas price specified by the user is automatically reverted to the default value if \r\n1. open any of screens to specify Recipient (e.g. Contacts). There is no need to select other recipient, just opening and closing the screen is enough to cause Gas price change\r\n2. open Assets screen. Also no need to select other asset\r\n\r\nNote that Gas limit value is not changed. So, 2 fields on Transaction screen behave in different way: Gas price is reverting to default value when Gas limit does not.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nValues in all fields on Send Transaction and Transaction Fee screens stay the same if \r\n1. open Assets screen but do not do any changes or select same asset as already selected\r\n2. open Recipient -> Contact and close it or select some recipient\r\n3. open Recipient -> Enter recipient value and close it or provide valid or invalid value for recipient address\r\n4. special case: Recipient -> scan QR there are 2 cases:\r\n4.1 Asset = ETH, scan QR code does not change asset and it stays ETH: we should keep values in Gas limit and Gas price as they were before scan\r\n4.2 Asset != ETH (so some token, e.g. SNT), scan QR: it's expected that Asset will be changed to ETH, amount field will be cleared. In this case we can revert values in Gas limit and Gas price to default values\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n1. If scan QR code when Asset = ETH then values in Gas limit and Gas price are reverted to default values automatically\r\n2. In all other cases only Gas price is reverted back to default value:\r\n2.1 if open Recipient -> Contacts, Recipient -> Enter recipient address \r\n2.2 if open Assets\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\nfrom 00:18 https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8500248/sessions/4394466347/?accessToken=Cw1vyX1bPFQuq9Z0e3Z33-2TqSU\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open Wallet -> Send transaction\r\n- Open Advanced and change values for Gas limit and Gas price\r\n- Open Assets do not change anything and close it. Check values in advanced\r\n- Repeat checks for modified Gas limit and Gas price specified in Expected behavior section\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly June 20\r\n* Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\n\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8500248/sessions/4394466347/?accessToken=Cw1vyX1bPFQuq9Z0e3Z33-2TqSU\">TestFairy: Status 0.9.21 (6078) @2018</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
